# Rendered outputs anywhere in the tree (commit only when explicitly intended)
**/*.html
**/*.pdf
**/*.docx
**/*.tex
**/*.aux
**/*.log
**/*.out
**/*.toc

# Some figures and references are legit PDFs/HTML downloads — these are
# tracked explicitly even though they match the patterns above. Use:
#   git add -f path/to/file.pdf
# to override the ignore rule when adding a real artifact.

